data.description:
As you cruise into this awesome community with a stellar trail park, pickle, basketball courts, event Ramada, you will see where the buyer & all pets can hang out!!  There is literally acreage in the amount of space to run, roll and play, in the sun or the shade, at this park.  So, do stop by or slow down and check it all out, then simply keep walking & come see us  on Gunderson!  The home is super clean, spacious, backs to a wash and therefore private, quiet and tranquil with distant mountain views & view fencing. Sellers have had a termite inspection and  addressed a few inspection critiques and made most all repairs, purchased new landscape rock for the yard, and replaced all carpeting.
Seller provided booties to keep the home pristine. The floorplan has that HIGHLY sought after 1st floor bedroom & restroom for guest or elderly that cant make the stairs. We have 3 different eating areas, 2 interior & 1 exterior living spaces, 3 garages & a blank backyard canvas awaiting your dreams and creativity!
